    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spiced meat-free mince</strong> over the<strong> cucumber & Greek cheese bulgur</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved chopped</strong> <strong>mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
